Plombières-les-Bains • Anti-stress Resort

   "Countless springs, torrents and streams feed pine and beech forests.
   In short, water, water, and more water "
   Letter from Guy de Maupassant to his mother about his visit to
   Plombieres-les-Bains.

Benefactress Waters since the ancient times

   Since ancient times, men and women from all over Northern Europe have
   come to take care of themselves in the warm and saving waters of
   Plombieres.
   Thus, over the centuries, the site attracts renowned visitors: writers,
   engineers, musicians and politicians. Montaigne, Berlioz and two
   generations of the imperial family have stayed there regularly. They
   appreciated the discreet and devoted nature of the population.
   Today, two thousand years later, the waters of Plombieres are
   recognized for their effectiveness in the treatment of diseases linked
   with the digestive system and rheumatism.

   Download our 2019 brochure


Anti-stress Resort

   The care lavished in Plombieres-les-Bains, combined with the mild and
   soothing air of the valley, rebalances in depth the organism and the
   nervous system.

Thermal Treatments

   Thermal medicine treats many chronic pathologies, painful constraints
   factors for which only long-term treatments are offered. Without any
   side effects, the thermal treatment is for everyone at any age!

   Read more

Balneotherapy

   Wish to relax and enjoy all the benefits of Plombieres Thermal Waters?
   Discover the 4 historic Spa Calodae baths and our wide range of face
   and body treatments, combining relaxation and spa expertise with our
   team of beauticians.

   Read more

Boutique

   How about a getaway in the heart of our green and relaxing valley? Book
   now on our online boutique your stays and your treatments at the
   Balneo-Roman Spa or gift this unique thermal spa experience to a loved
   one…

   Read more

Welcome to our restaurant L'Orangerie

   Read more

